title: A day in the life of self-quarantine | Haley Kim
description:
#quarantine #selfquarantine #quarantinevlog

A week ago I got back to Korea and have been being in self-quararinting for a week. During the time, I‚Äôve been working on my dissertation, reading and just trying to be productive even though it is hard. I am really honestly so grateful and privileged that I can still work from home as a Youtuber but a lot of peoples‚Äô lives are being affected. There is a lot of uncertainty, panic and anxiety going on.  I was also in the situation too and am still worried about my friends and people I care in UK and Europe. The best thing we can do is staying at home and there is not that much we can do apart from it. ‚ÄúWe can‚Äôt choose what happens to us but we can choose how to respond‚Äù. This is my favourite quote and I am trying to remind it every single day. I decided to take this time as self-improvement opportunity and knowing myself more as I am being alone at home. Hope you guys are all safe and I wish you take this time as another opportunity for yourself, family and people who you care. Please stay safe and sending so much love xx

title: Soft Fall Makeup ‚Ä¢ GRWM for Meetup | Haley Kim
description:
#softfallmakeup #autumnmakeup #softbrownmakeup


While I had a break from YouTube, I was seeking another way to communicate with you guys, so decided to do my first meet up in Korea. As there has been so much positive energy shared on my channel, I decided to title my first meetup #goodinspiration #Ï¢ãÏùÄÏòÅÍ∞ê. There I spoke about myself in depth, including things like how my life as a student in UK has been so far, any difficulties I have experienced as YouTuber. I also got the chance to share my makeup inspirations, favourite books, films and so much more!  My lovely viewers were listening to me so carefully and especially focused during the makeup demo. I will never forget those shining eyes.


I went to meet up #foundationfree because I wanted to show how my skin looks bare, in real life. So many others also came without foundation and shared their experiences of how their skin condidtion has improved to become so healthy!


Thank you guys for giving me positive energy and being a reason why I do this work.  I will definitely make more opportunities to meet you guys in real life. Next one will be London as I am coming back to the UK soon! So stay tuned ‚ù§Ô∏è
